  <main>
    <section class="intro">
      <h2>Welcome to the Sports Scheduler</h2>
      <p>
        Our Sports Scheduler application is designed to make organizing and joining sports sessions easy and efficient for both players and administrators. Whether you are an administrator managing various sports or a player looking for a game to join, this platform has you covered.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <h3>Features</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>For Administrators:</strong>
          <ul>
            <li>Create sports and manage sessions</li>
            <li>View reports on sessions and sports popularity</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>For Players:</strong>
          <ul>
            <li>Create or join sports sessions</li>
            <li>View sessions they have joined</li>
            <li>Cancel sessions with a reason</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mission">
      <h3>Our Mission</h3>
      <p>
        Our mission is to provide an easy-to-use, reliable platform where sports enthusiasts can connect, schedule games, and enjoy their favorite activities with friends and fellow players. We aim to make sports more accessible to everyone.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="contact">
